{"tid":1589062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1日 全民送鐘 Twitter #101burnwithus","createTime":"2019-09-23T06:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:39:50.000Z","uid":263217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ff69983f0d28354faa11d03d141f12c6e3a840","tid":1589062,"uid":263217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"10月1日 全港路祭習近平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n承巴打10月1全港路祭post，網上我地再賀一賀佢<br />\n<br />\n步驟<br />\n1) 打印一張有習維尼頭像圖<br />\n2) 準備手機拍片<br />\n3) 用不同方法燒著圖片，全程拍攝<br />\n4) 記得整熄個火<br />\n5) 上載片段至Twitter，hashtag<br />\n#101burnwithus #SaynotoCCP<br />\nFB IG都得，不過影響力有限，又易被起底<br />\n6) 廣泛comment至全球知名人士Twitter post，直到trend為止<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇<br />\n認同就推爆佢<br />\n<br />\n記住 記住 記住<br />\n小心唔好整響火警鐘<br />\n<br />\n10月1日<br />\n全民送鐘"},{"pid":"e1a39d0e5607f50c6c66cf8fa49722f8c31fcada","tid":1589062,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"5421a642a67c7ceb1d2cf93e6c4391d07e87934a","tid":1589062,"uid":325882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdc5cd3b434e6833790f2f3ed65bb3966ca68df5","tid":1589062,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"10月1 憤恨祖國分裂70年<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590087</a>"},{"pid":"a576a4bd0c6a75d2f18cb7e74147f0eb23bb2ac9","tid":1589062,"uid":188688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor